     H            Y.
     F** UEXR24 *********************************************
     F*  PROGRAM: EXSUB - CALCULATE KANBAN QTY              *
     F*  WRITTEN: JW (SRA) 2020.04.21                       *
     F*  JW       2020.04.28 ADD $ZAIS $ZAIK                *
     F*-----------------------------------------------------*
     F*  CALLING SEQ.
     F*                    CALL 'UEXR24'
     F*                    PARM           $ZAIS  15
     F*                    PARM           $ZAIK   5 2
     F*                    PARM           $MSET   8 0
     F*                    PARM           $CWGT   5 0
     F*                    PARM           $SCOE   3 2
     F*                    PARM           $LT     3 0
     F*                    PARM           $LOT    2 0
     F*                    PARM           $ADJ    3 0
     F*                    PARM           $KQTY   3 0
     F*                    PARM           $RTN    1
     F*  IN  $ZAIS  15    MATERIAL
     F*      $ZAIK   5 2  DIAMETER
     F*      $MSET   8 0  MONTHLY SET WGT
     F*      $CWGT   5 0  COIL WGT
     F*      $SCOE   3 2  SAFETY COEF.
     F*      $LT     3 0  LEAD TIME
     F*      $LOT    2 0  LOT SIZE
     F*      $ADJ    3 0  ADJUST QTY
     F*  OUT $KQTY   3 0  KANBAN QTY
     F*      $RTN    1A   ETURN CODE (OK:BLANK, *:ERROR)
     F*
      *===================================================
      * PARAMETER
      *===================================================
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           $ZAIS  15
     C                     PARM           $ZAIK   52
     C                     PARM           $MSET   80
     C                     PARM           $CWGT   50
     C                     PARM           $SCOE   32
     C                     PARM           $LT     30
     C                     PARM           $LOT    20
     C                     PARM           $ADJ    30
     C                     PARM           $KQTY   30
     C                     PARM           $RTN    1
      *===================================================
      *           MAIN ROUTINE
      *===================================================
     C                     Z-ADD0         $KQTY
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    $RTN
      * IF WGT=0,
     C           $CWGT     IFEQ 0
     C                     GOTO ENDP
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      * 1.GET DAYLY USAGE (WDAY)  -------------------
     C           $MSET     DIV  20        WKQTY  127H
     C           WKQTY     DIV  $CWGT     WDAY   127H
      *
      * 2.TENTATIVE KANBAN (TKQTY) ------------------
     C           WDAY      MULT $SCOE     WTQTY  127H
     C                     MULT $LT       WTQTY     H
      * KURIAGE (ROUND UP)
     C                     Z-ADDWTQTY     NUM3    30
     C           WTQTY     IFEQ NUM3
     C                     Z-ADDNUM3      TKQTY   30
     C                     ELSE
     C           NUM3      ADD  1         TKQTY
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      * 3.MULTIPLE MASHINE ADJ ----------------------
     C                     CALL 'UEXC28'
     C                     PARM           $ZAIS  15
     C                     PARM           $ZAIK   52
     C                     PARM           $MSET   80
     C                     PARM           $CWGT   50
     C                     PARM           @ADJ    30
     C                     ADD  @ADJ      TKQTY
      *
      * 4. ADD 1 IF MSET > 100  ---------------------  XXX
     C           TKQTY     IFEQ 1
     C           $MSET     ANDGE100
     C                     ADD  1         TKQTY
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      * 5.ADJUSTMENT (WADJ) -------------------------
     C           $LOT      SUB  1         WADJ    20
     C                     ADD  $ADJ      WADJ
      *
      * 6.FINAL KANBAN QTY --------------------------
     C           TKQTY     ADD  WADJ      $KQTY
      *
     C           ENDP      TAG
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INLR
     C                     RETRN
